			<div class="post" id="post-1327">
			<h2><a href="http://MadMoneyMachine.com/2009/01/22/mmm-143/" rel="bookmark" title="Permalink a MMM-143: Gingerbread Man">MMM-143: Gingerbread Man</a></h2>
			<p>Logic Pro. Gingerbread Man Geocache travel bug. Backing up your computer. Mint.com? Live CashBack worked. Non-systematic risk. Rick says Mish is full of mush. P/E not as good at P=E/i. Lazy Portfolios are not idiotic. Great risk, need long time. Tool: table of returns.</p>
<div>
<div>I ENCOURAGE you to <a href="http://phobos.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewPodcast?id=109739826">Download this show thru iTunes!</a> <a href="http://phobos.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewPodcast?id=109739826" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.madmoneymachine.com/images/subscribe_with_itunes.gif" alt="Subscribe with iTunes!" align="right" /> </a> But, if you just cannot deal with that then go ahead and Play the new show right now</div>
<div>
